Class Errortype

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ss.formula.functions.Fixed1ArgFunction
      • org.apache.poi.ss.formula.functions.Errortype
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function, Function1Arg

    public final class Errortype
extends Fixed1ArgFunction
    Implementation for the ERROR.TYPE() Excel function.

    Syntax:
    ERROR.TYPE(errorValue)

    Returns a number corresponding to the error type of the supplied argument.

    errorValueReturn Value
    #NULL!1
    #DIV/0!2
    #VALUE!3
    #REF!4
    #NAME?5
    #NUM!6
    #N/A!7
    everything else#N/A!
    Note - the results of ERROR.TYPE() are different to the constants defined in ErrorConstants.

    Author:
    Josh Micich
